And `_rust_i18n_lookup_fallback`:
```rust
pub fn _rust_i18n_lookup_fallback(locale: &str) -> Option<&str> {
    locale.rfind('-').map(|n| locale[..n].trim_end_matches("-x"))
}
```
Strips from last `-`. The `trim_end_matches("-x")` handles the `-x-private` extension. Good.

